i  172.22.76.109/32   via 172.18.1.54 on ltnet [lt_docker_ospf 17:41:06] * E2 (150/1/10000) [172.18.1.54]		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i  172.22.76.104/29   via 172.18.1.54 on ltnet [lt_docker_ospf 01:00:08] * I (150/2) [172.18.1.54]		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
